    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Atropine effects\nLethargy\n,\nagitation\n, flushing, dry mucous membranes, mydriasis,\nileus\n,\ntachycardia\nOpioid effects\nMiosis,\ncoma\n, respiratory depression,\nrespiratory arrest",
