    "Evaluation": {
      "text": "Diagnosis is based on history and signs of toxicity",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
      "links": []
    },
    "Management": {
      "text": "Maintain airway and support\nventilation\n, if needed\nNaloxone\n1-2mg IV for apnea, coma, or lethargy (may require repeat dosing)\nActivated charcoal\nshould be given promptly if available\nNo evidence for utility of\nphysostigmine",
      "subsections": {},
